{
  "texts": [
    "The application is divided into the control of machinery, display interfaces, programmable controllers and transmission lines.",
    "These are combined as \"control and execution modules.\"",
    "Hereby, it is shown how an implementation can be facilitated with the digital twin bridging the gap between the optimization results and actual operations in the terminal.",
    "Meanwhile, Hofmann and Branding (2019) also apply a simulation model with a dispatching algorithm based on the concept of starvation avoidance.",
    "The digital twin is used to evaluate different results of the dispatching algorithm in combination with (near) real time data from IoT devices."
  ]
}